### Context

Stack Overflow’s annual Developer Survey is the largest and most comprehensive survey of people who code around the world. Each year, Stack Overflow field a survey covering everything from developers’ favourite technologies to their job preferences.


### Content

Individual responses on the Developer Survey fielded by Stack Overflow 2011 - 2015
